- daemon support (for main- and subprocesses)
- use serialized objects between processes
- integrate other process types (not php)
- kill and terminate processes
- intergrate more communication types between processes: 4. pipe, sqlite, memcached, filesystem ...
- integration exception handling from sub- thrown to mainprocess
- handleevent time interval configurable
- houston definition in external and multiple files (so houston can be run from inside a project)